query:
insert into tiny_auth_authorization_code (
    client_id,
    user,
    redirect_uri,
    scope,
    code,
    insertion_time,
    authentication_time,
    nonce,
    pkce_challenge,
    pkce_challenge_method)
select
    ?1,
    ?2,
    ?3,
    ?4,
    ?5,
    ?8,
    ?6,
    ?7,
    ?9,
    ?10
